&lt;li&gt;Working knowledge of IP networking fundamentals and Linux command line interfaces.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate effectively with cross-functional teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior military or overseas contracting experience.&lt;/li&gt;
