&lt;p&gt;Drive technical decision making by partnering on optimal setup, architecture, and integration of Claude into the customer&#39;s existing infrastructure. Demonstrate solutions to technical roadblocks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
