&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;2367&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot;&gt;What we look for:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Extensive experience in navigating complex customer engagements and the sales lifecycle within a technical pre-sales environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Proven ability to lead strategic business discussions with C-level executives to build strong relationships, orchestrate internal teams, and influence outcomes that drive long-term customer success.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Strong aptitude for identifying and prioritising key business use cases, strategic resource allocation, and investment strategies to maximise impact.&lt;/li&gt;
