&lt;p&gt;FEQ227R207&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Field Engineering Manager, you will lead a talented team of technical pre-sales Solutions Architects and Solutions Engineers based in France. You’ll play a key leadership role at the intersection of technology and business, helping our teams design value-based solutions and drive growth through effective collaboration with Sales.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll coach your team to communicate complex ideas clearly, support strategic sales cycles, and build strong partnerships with customers and stakeholders across large organisations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The impact you will have:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead, mentor, and develop a high-performing pre-sales team in France.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Foster an inclusive and collaborative culture that reflects Databricks’ values of customer obsession, teamwork, and diversity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Sales to drive growth through solution- and value-based selling.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enhance team effectiveness by establishing best practices that improve efficiency and focus on business impact.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build trusted relationships with customer executives and strategic partners.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate across teams—including Marketing, Sales, and Services—to ensure seamless implementation and customer success.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent Databricks as part of the regional leadership team and contribute to building our brand and presence in the market.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What we look for:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience managing technical teams in Big Data, Cloud, or SaaS environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A track record of leading, mentoring, and scaling pre-sales or technical field organisations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understanding of consumption-based business models.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to collaborate effectively with Sales and other cross-functional leaders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong communication and interpersonal skills—fluent in English and native-level French.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Technical background in Data Engineering, Databases, or Data Science (consulting experience is a plus).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passion for data, AI, and cloud technologies and the ability to articulate their business value clearly.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Note: Location for the role is in Paris (i.e. within commutable distance).&lt;/p&gt;
