&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hire, train, and nurture a team of Solutions Architects to foster a culture of excellence and innovation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Empower your team to navigate technical complexities, identify key use cases, and build compelling proofs of concept.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Foster a culture of continuous learning and development within the team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1648&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sales Excellence | Activated Logos | Databricks consumption&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive the activation of new customers by guiding the Solutions Architect team in qualifying use cases, building customer trust, and navigating complex enterprise deals from discovery to close.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead your team in establishing themselves as trusted advisors throughout the customer life-cycle.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead your team to excel in technical qualifications, proof of concepts, architecture discussions, product demonstrations, and implementation plans.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Play a crucial role in achieving technical wins in complex sales cycles.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1648&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Customer Success and Value Delivery:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure customer success by helping them succeed with Databricks solutions and delivering outsized value to their businesses.&lt;/li&gt;
